# Git Commit Rules

## Author
Always use this author for every commit in this repo:
```
Ivo M <ivomod@users.noreply.github.com>
```

Set it explicitly on every commit:
```bash
git commit --author="Ivo M <ivomod@users.noreply.github.com>" -m "..."
```

## Commit Messages
- Do NOT add `Co-authored-by: Cursor` or any Cursor-related trailers
- Do NOT add `Made-with: Cursor` or any similar lines
- Keep messages clean: subject line only, or subject + body with no AI tool footers
